704156f-a.title: Brooklyn: Evergreen Avenue - Palmetto Street
704156f-a.text:
Evergreen Ave., west sid:, east from, but not including Palmetto
Street. In the foreground, are frame dwellings Nos. 451-453. Also seen
is the Second German Baptist Church.
September 9, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
